release_note: Bug fixes. New fonts and quotes.

Bug fixes and stability improvements. Refreshed color scheme for a better visual experience. Adjustable text size options for improved readability. Performance optimizations for faster loading times. User interface refinements based on user feedback.

In this version we have made some exciting updates to improve your experience with the app. Here s a rundown of what s new: New App icon: We have given the app a fresh new look with a brand new icon. Color update: We have made some updates to the color scheme to make the app more visually appealing and easy on the eyes. iOS 16 bug fixes: We have fixed some bugs and compatibility issues with the latest version of iOS to ensure a seamless user experience. We hope these updates make your experience with the app even better. If you have any feedback or suggestions please reach out to our support team. Thank you for using our app!
